<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.6.9">
<l>cantamāy camaya mākic camayavaim pūta māki</l>
<l>yantamā yāti yāki yarumaṟai yavaiyu māṉāy</l>
<l>mantamār poḻilka ṭōṟum maṭamayi lālum nāṅkai</l>
<l>kantamār kāva ḷantaṇ pāṭiyāy kaḷaika ṇīyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who are prosody, who are [its] conventions,</l>
<l rend="indent">who are the five elements [associated with] the conventions,</l>
<l>You who are the end, who are the beginning,</l>
<l rend="indent">and who became the rare Vedas, too,</l>
<l>You of the cool hamlet of fragrant Kāvaḷam in Nāṅkai</l>
<l>Where simple peacocks call in every dense grove, only you are [our] refuge.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
